These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: grapes, eggplant
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the person eating eggplant##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | eggplant   | grapes  |
| Sport   | skiing | skateboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, nectarine
2 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the hamster is not the person eating nectarine##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | cabbage | nectarine      |
| Pet    | hamster  | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
