.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, photographer
2 different pets are kept: horse, frog
1. the videographer is in an odd position##4
2. the videographer is not the owner of the frog##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | videographer | photographer |
| Pet   | horse       | frog       |

